00:38:17.530 --> 00:38:21.570
government-oriented branch.

00:38:21.570 --> 00:38:24.860
It's the cause for a
lot of the headaches

00:38:24.860 --> 00:38:26.770
we have dealt with
in the city too.

00:38:26.770 --> 00:38:29.620
