00:41:16.080 --> 00:41:17.496
I wonder if there's
an opportunity

00:41:17.496 --> 00:41:21.390
to offer your goods for sale
within Two Boots, right?

00:41:21.390 --> 00:41:22.140
Prepare the food.

00:41:22.140 --> 00:41:22.848
Bring it to them.

00:41:22.848 --> 00:41:23.610
Let them sell it.

00:41:23.610 --> 00:41:26.880
That will bring way more foot
traffic into their store.

00:41:26.880 --> 00:41:29.370
Maybe they'll get on
your side that way.

00:41:29.370 --> 00:41:30.140
I would go there.

00:41:30.140 --> 00:41:30.940
I also live in Jersey City.

