to do that, and largely

00:52:05.320 --> 00:52:08.110
at the expense of that was
because of the permit that

00:52:08.110 --> 00:52:12.580
was-- this sticker
that was on the truck.

00:52:12.580 --> 00:52:16.770
We got really screwed
in that transaction

00:52:16.770 --> 00:52:21.790
in that when we bought the food
truck from its previous owners,

00:52:21.790 --> 00:52:26.490
the permittee who saw that the
food truck was changing hands

00:52:26.490 --> 00:52:30.010
and who had already been paid
in full for the next two years

00:52:30.010 --> 00:52:32.540
of the rental of
his permit decided

00:52:32.540 --> 00:52:35.110
that he could rent
that permit to somebody

00:52:35.110 --> 00:52:37.030
else at the same time.

00:52:37.030 --> 00:52:39.550
